{"tid":136612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲醉酒休班靚女警襲擊途人罪成","createTime":"2017-02-27T07:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T15:01:46.000Z","uid":48093,"like":18,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"255d639a3b65957889b2f76befbfed5fbc00719a","tid":136612,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170227/large/1488180001_490c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170227%2Flarge%2F1488180001_490c.jpg&h=8c946b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年輕休班女警於去年7月8日深夜時份在街頭醉酒，期間疑不滿兩名下班踏單車經過的女侍應說話大聲，先後襲擊兩人，當女警得悉對方打算報警時更情緒激動指「你報報報乜&times;嘢警，我就係差人」。事後女警被控兩項普通襲擊罪，裁判官今判被告第二項罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n據證人指事件報警及兩人被送院驗傷後，被告袁樂欣（25歲）曾一度在醫院哭著跪地道歉求原諒。"},{"pid":"4306993bef8b42555da1fb39d5b67b09755ec6b5","tid":136612,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0793f2daa29a4f14609a3e35d8fb87c034a81c6f","tid":136612,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:30:28.000Z","msg":"猶太人+1"},{"pid":"151cd088d6593684051f6d257b24fba895c25498","tid":136612,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be7a450def8e3ddd2606ef1f7facb99d3dfa320","tid":136612,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"靚女警？邊度呀？"},{"pid":"a3993866d3b55da2c4f0fe8750e550120316a7e0","tid":136612,"uid":85498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"侍應唔應該咁大聲 先撩者賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328d24f2f1fe521fb449a9d27cdaabc1ec1c35a1","tid":136612,"uid":77336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":